{"tid":2425270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國「養套殺」台灣農　剛開始時給台農方便　現在開始殺起來","createTime":"2021-02-27T08:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T11:26:53.000Z","uid":261647,"like":231,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"aa21c4ce5bb93a112d9ac5a0e296cda3efbb27ca","tid":2425270,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/letsupupup/posts/810483899675609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fletsupupup%2Fposts%2F810483899675609&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=abab37d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/letsupupup/posts/810483899675609</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：鄉民挺起來<br />\n<br />\n我認為鳳梨被中國以有害蟲的理由整批拒買，台灣長年安逸於中國收購的農產品而被牢牢綁架，就是他們執行多年的「養套殺」，現在要開始殺了。<br />\n<br />\n日本進口台灣芒果，一律需要經過熱蒸熟處理，就是為了防止東方果實蠅蟲卵，而外銷中國的水果都沒有這一步驟，剛開始你會覺得很方便、友善，但結果就是可以一句「有蟲」，就全部拒買。<br />\n<br />\n這麼多年來台灣農業熱愛與中國貿易與技術交流，除了外銷農產品，更將大量的種植技術、品種、經驗智慧輸出到中國，一直以來都毫無戒心。當他們自己都會種了，幹嘛還要跟你買呢？<br />\n<br />\n台灣人也該醒醒了，中國只會把你用完就丟，沒有任何情誼道義可言的，鳳梨整批拒買可能只是第一槍。"},{"pid":"72d239bacf58f6c8449b9226c9619fb340564a0a","tid":2425270,"uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/laichinan/status/1365317788596756485?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flaichinan%2Fstatus%2F1365317788596756485%3Fs%3D21&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=039c3edb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flaichinan%2Fstatus%2F1365317788596756485%3Fs%3D21&h=6ae78b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/laichinan/status/1365317788596756485?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/laichinan/status/1365333542486437891?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flaichinan%2Fstatus%2F1365333542486437891%3Fs%3D21&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ed983